OL,3,CAverage price of pint to surge above
OL,4,C#5 due to April cost hikes, say beer
OL,5,Cbosses
OL,7,FThe average price of a pint of beer is
OL,8,Fset to surge past #5 for the first
OL,9,Ftime due to cost hikes hitting the
OL,10,Fsector next month, according to
OL,11,Findustry bosses.
OL,13,FPub sector chiefs have warned that
OL,14,Fprices for customers will have to
OL,15,Fincrease in order to help keep venues
OL,16,Frunning in the face of higher labour
OL,17,Fcosts.
