OL,3,CAverage price of pint to surge above
OL,4,C#5 due to April cost hikes, say beer
OL,5,Cbosses
OL,7,FThe British Beer and Pub Association
OL,8,Fsaid the average cost of a pint in the
OL,9,FUK is expected to rise by around 21p
OL,10,Fas a result.
OL,12,FThe research, commissioned alongside
OL,13,FFrontier Economics, showed that pub
OL,14,Ffirms are expecting to raise the
OL,15,Faverage price of a pint from #4.80 to
OL,16,F#5.01.
OL,18,FThis comes amid a raft of cost
OL,19,Fincreases linked to last October's
OL,20,Fbudget, which will come into force in
OL,21,FApril.
