OL,3,CAverage price of pint to surge above
OL,4,C#5 due to April cost hikes, say beer
OL,5,Cbosses
OL,7,FFirms will face increases to the
OL,8,Fnational minimum wage, a rise in
OL,9,Fnational insurance rates and a
OL,10,Fdecrease in the threshold at which
OL,11,Ffirms start paying out national
OL,12,Finsurance.
OL,14,FBusiness rates discounts for firms in
OL,15,Fthe sector will also be cut from 75%
OL,16,Fto 40% from April.
OL,18,FThe net cost of autumn budget
OL,19,Fannouncements across the beer and pub
OL,20,Fsector is approximately #650 million
OL,21,Fin total, the trade body said.
